709267f-a.title: Manhattan: 6th Avenue - King Street.
709267f-a.text:
Sixth Avenue, west side, from King (left) to West Houston Streets. This building line was originally the westerly side of the former Congress Street. It lost its identity in 1928 on the extension of the Avenue southward. For photos of same see files uhder the Congress
Street heading.
April 30, 1940
P. L. Sperr
